snippet.title: Colossal Cave - Launch Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10004303

From the designer of Kings Quest and Phantasmagoria Experience Colossal Cave reimagined by Roberta Williams, the thrilling new adventure game. Launching January 19th on PlayStation 5. Explore a mysterious underground world and discover its secrets, hidden treasures and solve challenging puzzles in this immersive cave-exploring experience. Don't miss out on the fun

#ps5games #ps5

*Footage captured on PC.  Not all Images Appear In-Game.*
